    <p class="text-gray-300"><span class="math">$A = \\alpha + A_{\\gamma}\\gamma + A_{\\delta}\\delta + A(x) + \\cdots \\qquad B = \\beta + B_{\\gamma}\\gamma + B_{\\delta}\\delta + B(x) + \\cdots</span>$</p>

