    <p class="text-gray-300"><span class="math">$\\sum_{i=0}^{m} a_i u_i(x) \\cdot \\sum_{i=0}^{m} a_i v_i(x) = \\sum_{i=0}^{m} a_i w_i(x) + C_h(x) t(x).</span>$</p>

